---
title: Pesto & Macadamia Crusted Salmon with Honey Glazed Baby Carrots & Pear Salad
description: We all know honey makes carrots better, but let us share this gem with you – roasting carrots with honey makes them completely
irresistible. We guess it’s a bit like adding a macadamia crust to salmon, taking it from tasty to out-of-this-world delicious!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/macadamia-pesto-crusted-salmon-3cea0abb.jpg
